oint of Totto, and I think something they do better than Ippudo. ?Slurp slurp. No surprise a really legit place for ramen in NYC. ?The wait time and the "C" rating do bring it down a notch for me, but it's pretty much splitting hairs between the other NYC ramen champ. Will have to come back before winter is up.
